            <span>Sisters</span>
            <span>About Us</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="section1">
            <h1 style="transform: translateY(30px); font-size: 50px;">A Word From Our President</h1>
            <div class="presidentimg" style="position: absolute"></div>
            <div class="presidentname" style="padding-left: 35%; position: absolute; font-size: 30px;">
                <p style="font-style: italic">Kebar Geleta</p>
            </div>
            <div class="presidentwords" style="padding-top: 3%; padding-left: 35%; position: absolute font-size: 30px;">
                <p style="font-size: 30px"><strong style="font-size: 50px">N</strong>u Delta has provided a home away from home for many of our members. The<br> sense of community and brotherhood that everyone shows has been an inspiration for<br> me and my time in the fraternity. So far, giving back as president has been a difficult<br> journey, but rewarding nonetheless. It brings me joy to know that my actions as our<br> community leader could make MIT more comfortable for some. Moving forward,<br> Nu Delta's brothers plan to continue to foster a safe space for their fellow members<br> and a model of exemplary character on campus. </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class = "section2">
            <h1 style="transform: translateY(200px); font-size: 50px;">Brothers</h1>
            <div class = "brothersimg" style = "position: absolute;"></div>
            <div class = "brotherstext" style = "text-align: center;">
                <p style = "transform: translateY(950px);font-size: 30px"><strong style="font-size: 50px;">T</strong>he brothers of Nu Delta share a tight bond that brings<br>us together and promotes our success as individuals.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class = "section3">
            <h1 style = "transform: translateY(975px); font-size: 50px;">Our House</h1>
            <div class = "houseimg" style = "position: absolute;"></div>
            <div class = "housetext" style = "text-align: center;">
                <p style = "transform: translateY(1720px); font-size: 30px"><strong style="font-size: 50px;">M</strong>any of the brothers reside in our lovely 4 story mansion located at<br>460 Beacon Street in Boston. For many of the brothers, this is where our<br>fondest MIT memories are made, so we take great pride in our house.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
